      "title": "NO shortage of essentials",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Ministry of Trade and Commerce says there is NO shortage of essential goods in the country.",
        "Secretary to the Ministry of Commerce S.T. Kodikara said there are sufficient stocks of essential goods in the country such as Rice, Flour, Sugar, Dhal, and Sprats.",
        "Further, steps have also been taken to re-import the essential goods according to the requirements.",
        "The Secretary further said 10 commodities have been identified as essential goods."
      ],
